Tue Aug  8 06:25:55 UTC 2023 - Michael Vetter <mvetter@suse.com>

- Update to 0.4.2:
  New Features:
  * Add flags to configure the compression level
    --level to precisely set the compression level #372
    --fast and --slow #374
  * Add --format option #341
  Improvements:
