- Update to 0.4.1:
  New Features:
  * Add cli option to (de)compress quietly #325
  Improvements:
  * Allow ouch to decompress archive into existing folder #321
  * Accept inserting subcommand-independent flags in any position #329
  * Improve extension parsing logic #330
