Thu Dec  1 09:11:10 UTC 2022 - Michael Vetter <mvetter@suse.com>

- Update to 0.4.0:
  * More than 15 bug fixes (including major bugs).
  * New accessible mode.
  * Added list command.
  * Added support for .lz4 and .sz (snappy).
  * Infer file type while decompressing via MIME types.
